Thanks to Lucas Rocha, Iain Holmes, and Jens Granseuer for improvements
in this version.

        * No need to symlink to .desktop files (Lucas)
        * Fixes to compositor's dealings with overlay windows (Iain)
        * C89 fixes (Jens)

