  Miloslav Trmac (cs), Kostas Papadimas (el), Adam Weinberger (en_CA),
  Francisco Javier F. Serrador (es), Ilkka Tuohela (fi), Christophe
  Merlet (RedFox) (fr), Ignacio Casal Quinteiro (gl), Ankit 
